definition: Wen county in Longnan 隴南|陇南[Long3 nan2], Gansu

sentences.english: Another injury was reported in Wenxian County of the northwestern Gansu Province, which borders Qingchuan.
sentences.chinese: 另一名傷者在甘肅西北部與青川接壤的文縣。

sentences.english: The Yangshan gold deposit is located in Wenxian, Gansu Province.
sentences.chinese: 陽山金礦牀位於甘肅省文縣。

sentences.english: County is a remote Fam, a treasure-house full of magic.
sentences.chinese: 文縣是一處偏僻祕境，一塊充滿神奇的寶地。

sentences.english: Among them, Tylototriton wenxianensis is of a special species of Gansu.
sentences.chinese: 其中，文縣疣螈爲甘肅特有種。
